- **Where:** `## [Unreleased]` only—`### Added` / `Changed` / `Fixed` / `Removed` ([Keep a Changelog](https://keepachangelog.com/)); one idea per bullet.
- **Don’t:** add dated `## [x.y.z]` blocks (use `just release` / `scripts/release.py` unless the user asked); **don’t edit** footer compare/tag links (`release.py` needs `[Unreleased]: …compare/v*…...HEAD`).
- **Never skip `[Unreleased]`** for edits to `include/argsbarg/builtins.hpp`, `include/argsbarg/argsbarg.hpp` (completion/help/dispatch), `scripts/release.py`, or `.github/workflows`—add a bullet unless the change is strictly invisible (say so in the reply).
- **Before you stop:** if the “must” cases in `description` applied and `CHANGELOG.md` wasn’t updated, fix that or state why you skipped.
